    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really wonderful shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it runs super smoothly and looks great both inside and out. It's the perfect fit for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for plenty more adventures. I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
