    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies. The double VANOS system has been recently serviced, ensuring optimal cam timing across the 8,000 RPM rev range. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with upgraded poly-bushings and documented rear subframe reinforcement. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a well-loved performance vehicle, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a raw, analog connection to the road. Recent fluid analysis and valve adjustment confirm this high-revving powerhouse is ready for the track or the canyons.",
